{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d0d70061c0","title":"毛泽东撰郑州会议纪要","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"35995f10d1","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"d0d70061c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d32e5b5610","type":"title","text":"毛泽东撰郑州会议纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"5b1813e7d0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年二月二十七日，在郑州举行了中央政治局扩大会议。会议进行了七天，三月五日结束。到会者，中央二十人，省、市、区党委第一书记二十七人，共四十七人。会议的主题是人民公社问题。首先由毛泽东同志讲了他的意见，然后进行了几次讨论。结果如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"112160d285","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)同意毛泽东同志的意见。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"d2cf32a497","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)规定了如下十四句话作为当前整顿和建设人民公社的方针。这十四句话是：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"0dc812e474","type":"paragraph","text":"统一领导，队为基础；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"1b591bbd94","type":"paragraph","text":"分级管理，权力下放；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"905bcc614f","type":"paragraph","text":"三级核算，各计盈亏；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"7bbe4f30f5","type":"paragraph","text":"分配计划，由社决定；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"b7c22a9e18","type":"paragraph","text":"适当积累，合理调剂；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"b9bac8d6ed","type":"paragraph","text":"物资劳动，等价交换；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"c2fc60232f","type":"paragraph","text":"按劳分配，承认差别。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"},{"id":"c58b874620","type":"paragraph","text":"(三)起草了一个关于人民公社管理体制的若干规定(草案)。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0"}],"page":{"id":"8c86ffb866","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d0d70061c0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}